sample_description:
Field Review - Addition / Alteration - Interior alterations to repair fire and water damage to floors 1 to 3 of this existing hotel at this mixed use building on this site.

Revision #1:
1. To move hallway wall to further renovate all Bathrooms and modify their layouts upgrading plumbing fixtures and barrier free walk-in shower stalls in all levels;
2. To upgrade all electrical and lighting fixtures, fire alarm system, internet, wifi and security systems;
3. To install new flooring and replace all guest room entry doors with 36"wide doors;
4. To reconfigure some guest rooms and entry lobby areas, lower and upper lobby;
5. To renovate existing rear basement areas for Laundry, employee lunch room, and office;
6. To demolish existing bar lounge to become a vacant tenant space for future same use;
7. To provide business center for guest use on first level and browsing area in lower lobby for guest uses, and change of use from part of one hotel suite to retail CRU on the 2nd floor;
8. To add: mech, electrical, and structural drawings to the current fire repair and revision scope of work;
9. To provide entrance to the future bar/lounge from the side of the building;
10. To change the permit Architect of record, CRP, and applicant.

OK for Field Review per D.Holbrook

Letters of Assurance:
